<?php

$curl = curl_init();

curl_setopt_array($curl, [
  CURLOPT_URL => "https://upload.api.synthesia.io/v2/assets",
  CURLOPT_RETURNTRANSFER => true,
  CURLOPT_ENCODING => "",
  CURLOPT_MAXREDIRS => 10,
  CURLOPT_TIMEOUT => 30,
  CURLOPT_HTTP_VERSION => CURL_HTTP_VERSION_1_1,
  CURLOPT_CUSTOMREQUEST => "POST",
  CURLOPT_POSTFIELDS => "data:image/jpeg;name=auditivo.jpg;base64,",
  CURLOPT_HTTPHEADER => [
    "Authorization: f27ca08825df962fceb1b7c4c9f03996",
    "Content-Type: image/jpeg",
    "accept: application/json"
  ],
]);

$response = curl_exec($curl);
$err = curl_error($curl);

curl_close($curl);

if ($err) {
  echo "cURL Error #:" . $err;
} else {
  echo $response;
}
